OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779279069
OL,3,CProtests held against plans to scrap
OL,4,Csome jury trials
OL,6,FAmong the protesters was retired
OL,7,FMagistrate and member of the national
OL,8,Fparole board Deborah Hinton OBE, who
OL,9,Fsays the jury system has "been in
OL,10,Fplace for 800 years" and we are now
OL,11,Fmarching "towards an authoritarian
OL,12,Fstate".
OL,14,FShe added: "How they decide before the
OL,15,Fcase has even got to the courts who's
OL,16,Fgoing to be getting a sentence of less
OL,17,Fthan three years - your guess is as
OL,18,Fgood as mine."
OL,20,F"The changes they're making are taking
OL,21,Faway our freedoms."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779279069
OL,3,CProtests held against plans to scrap
OL,4,Csome jury trials
OL,6,FCampaigners want the government to
OL,7,Fconsider other reforms to bring down
OL,8,Fthe backlog, like opening more courts
OL,9,For increasing sitting days.
OL,11,FShriya Shan was working locally and
OL,12,Fdecided to join the protest after
OL,13,Fspeaking to some of the campaigners.
OL,14,FShe said she "firmly believes it's
OL,15,Fimportant to keep juries".
OL,17,FShe said: "It's a representation of
OL,18,Fthe people's voices - our voices - in
OL,19,Fa system that we pay taxes for."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779279069
OL,3,CProtests held against plans to scrap
OL,4,Csome jury trials
OL,6,FCampaigner Oliver Baines thinks the
OL,7,Fremoval of juries in some trials
OL,8,F"won't make a difference" to the
OL,9,Fproblems facing the justice system.
OL,11,F"The problem is with the courts" said
OL,12,FMr Baines, "there's not enough sitting
OL,13,Fdays, not enough judges, not enough
OL,14,Fcourts available, defendants not
OL,15,Fturning up from prison on time,
OL,16,Fpaperwork not being ready, endless
OL,17,Fdelays..."
OL,19,F"Juries did not create this crisis,
OL,20,Fand removing them will not solve it."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779279069
OL,3,CProtests held against plans to scrap
OL,4,Csome jury trials
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice says the most
OL,7,Fserious of cases - such as rape,
OL,8,Fmurder and manslaughter - would be
OL,9,Fheard by a jury, and these measures
OL,10,Fare only necessary because of years of
OL,11,Fchronic underfunding by successive
OL,12,Fgovernments.
OL,14,F"Over 90% of criminal cases are
OL,15,Falready dealt with in magistrates'
OL,16,Fcourts ` fairly ` without juries.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779279069
OL,3,CProtests held against plans to scrap
OL,4,Csome jury trials
OL,6,F"It is only by pulling every lever at
OL,7,Four disposal - pragmatic structural
OL,8,Freform, record financial investment
OL,9,Fand modernisation - that we can drive
OL,10,Fdown the backlog."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
